### TAR and GZIP Commands (Copy-Paste Friendly)

Create a `.tar` archive

$ tar cvf archive.tar file_or_folder

Extract `.tar` archive

$ tar xvf archive.tar

Compress `.tar` using gzip

$ gzip archive.tar

Uncompress `.tar.gz`

$ gzip -d archive.tar.gz

or

$ gunzip archive.tar.gz

-----------------------

Create `.tar.gz` directly

$ tar czvf archive.tar.gz file_or_folder

Extract `.tar.gz` directly

$ tar xzvf archive.tar.gz



